{"tid":1012282,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"韓國瑜用「指腹為婚」形容台灣與中國的關係  顏擇雅說：抵觸北京\"兩岸一家親\"口號","createTime":"2019-02-07T12:43:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-20T01:08:25.000Z","uid":35790,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4dfb6fadd867bc262bd77735c78e550a70a1f9e7","tid":1012282,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T12:43:34.000Z","msg":"作家神解韓國瑜「指腹為婚」說：抵觸兩岸一家親<br />\n<br />\n2019-02-07 <br />\n <br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕高雄市長韓國瑜接受媒體專訪時，形容台灣與中國的關係是「指腹為婚」，引發論戰。作家顏擇雅從另類角度分析韓國瑜說法，提到中國共產黨上台不久便廢除包括指腹婚在內的封建婚姻傳統，隨即引發離婚潮，諷刺韓國瑜是不是暗指「兩岸就算勉強統一，終究要離婚？」<br />\n<br />\n顏擇雅在臉書上寫道，中共最自傲的成就之一，就是在1950年制定「婚姻法」，掃除封件婚姻傳統。依據法律，只要其中一方主張當初結婚非出於自由意志便可離婚，「指腹為婚」的婚約也無效，造成50年代中期一波離婚潮。<br />\n<br />\n顏擇雅說，<span style=\"color: red;\">她不知道韓國瑜「指腹為婚」的說法是腦袋太封建，還是「別有居心」，暗指兩岸就算勉強統一，終究要離婚？</span>認為韓的引申含意不就是「主張兩岸終須統一的都是中共認定需要思想改造的封建遺毒？」<br />\n<br />\n顏擇雅補充，<span style=\"color: red;\">韓的說法也抵觸了北京「兩岸一家親」的口號，因為不是一家人才可以結婚，婚後才變成一家人，因此，說兩岸是指腹為婚，代表目前不是一家人。</span><br />\n&lt;自由時報&gt;&gt;"},{"pid":"e86ac9a7be663f344537a1d34ff86f7091658b2a","tid":1012282,"uid":35790,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T12:45:25.000Z","msg":"近親不宜結婚<br />\n否則生bb可能有問題"},{"pid":"a24da19a8f2ba7f702caa7d0a716eb8256bb37cd","tid":1012282,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T12:49:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d98f2c01e22568e92f322acdea914cbd4d85e08c","tid":1012282,"uid":135409,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T12:55:38.000Z","msg":"亂倫咪生左你個弱智仔咯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"350e7adb6a1bf2f4126f295d6ca0275c97b918dd","tid":1012282,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T23:39:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a7349488dac34404d7a6a68e7a2e5d5d9087bf5","tid":1012282,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T00:16:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0d226dfb0d2f08f9984e8edd82df034b97241be","tid":1012282,"uid":4942,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T00:23:48.000Z","msg":"因為不是一家人才可以結婚，婚後才變成一家人，因此，說兩岸是指腹為婚，代表目前不是一家人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n串到佢一棟都無"},{"pid":"4609f046a09f1e44ae3c978581b39f1b687fcefd","tid":1012282,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e86ac9a7be663f344537a1d34ff86f7091658b2a","tid":1012282,"uid":35790,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T12:45:25.000Z","msg":"近親不宜結婚<br />\n否則生bb可能有問題"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T12:40:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"152d9748e18befb01cb3f29aed2b739d3b7178cd","tid":1012282,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T01:08:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}